This is a **Course Registration Form** for an online learning platform.  
It is built using **HTML5** and **CSS3** and demonstrates proper use of semantic elements, form validation, and user-friendly design.

---

## ðŸš€ Features
- Collects **personal information** (name, email, phone, date of birth, profile picture)
